{"tid":2104417,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[播毒師]鄭若驊：法律人員豁免檢疫　有助香港成為內企集資中心","createTime":"2020-07-12T02:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T03:45:09.000Z","uid":51271,"like":19,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"43ddb55417268e3672fe66e4f89c62eb03879fbc","tid":2104417,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:59:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537263-20200712.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537263-20200712.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNnjHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=d84c32de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537263-20200712.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1be1a182\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537263-20200712.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊表示，新型肺炎疫情造成史無前例的衝擊，政府有必要採取果斷的措施防止情況惡化，律政司會留意法律及爭議解決業界的需要，提供適切的支援。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>鄭若驊在網誌表示，面對疫情第三波，需要調整和更新策略，以減輕損害，預備迎接新常態。她表示，律政司早前已為合資格的法律執業者、仲裁員或調解員，提供豁免強制檢疫的機制，並已擴大豁免，讓多一些業界人士受惠，進一步協助法律及爭議解決業界，處理重大商業交易的相關工作。</strong>她表示，現時很多上市工作都與內地有關，相信措施有助香港繼續成為內地企業籌集資金的中心。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，在第二輪「防疫抗疫基金」下設立的「法律科技基金」，已接獲超過290份申請，司法機構亦擴大使用視像會議設施，已將申請截止日期延至本月26日；協助律師購買資訊科技設備時，可以考慮司法機構推出的「綜合法院案件管理系統」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，她表示，已推出的「新型冠狀病毒網上爭議解決計劃」，讓爭議雙方通過網上平台，解決相關爭議，有助紓緩法院民事索償的案件量，亦可為調解員和仲裁員帶來就業機會。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">原來你都有份播毒</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9ebb7099b72e1f029dc94567e905f588a4b934c5","tid":2104417,"uid":250775,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:59:46.000Z","msg":"鄭司長用心良苦攬炒，時代會還佢一個公道"},{"pid":"8618bb03925b4f4a492ea60b43693fef88b48a32","tid":2104417,"uid":63311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9ebb7099b72e1f029dc94567e905f588a4b934c5","tid":2104417,"uid":250775,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:59:46.000Z","msg":"鄭司長用心良苦攬炒，時代會還佢一個公道"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:00:28.000Z","msg":"去英國都比中共的返香港"},{"pid":"26adf14df9c9c16ae71558bffe15813e3e8c95b0","tid":2104417,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:00:46.000Z","msg":"播毒司司長鄭若驊"},{"pid":"bbf3dda3c55779a63729844c85837f5f7d48373b","tid":2104417,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb06a79b93482be6455271697df1f7ddb1d6c711","tid":2104417,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5523f636dd31299627c6f4cc784eefec959630","tid":2104417,"uid":103050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:05:43.000Z","msg":"成個港共有邊個無份播毒？"},{"pid":"f461263ecb1d4a43f7e670dea60f8d8083ef9846","tid":2104417,"uid":345459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:06:23.000Z","msg":"肥驊 利害"},{"pid":"77bc40f87e332a200e7957673139f2397892be41","tid":2104417,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:13:39.000Z","msg":"原來讀law嘅會自動抵抗武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4dbf4d26aa6e04aa94d782273ad7b4d4e2d9eb","tid":2104417,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:28:33.000Z","msg":"仲想集資？"},{"pid":"46abb71e6c64485de93d5e3b8f0e3102d02e0e07","tid":2104417,"uid":128923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T03:29:55.000Z","msg":"政府唔鳩理佢d 政治任務，講句野都可以錯timing 到咁，難怪直接用國安治港算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/do